    <content><![CDATA[<p>说句话</p>
<span id="more"></span>


<h2 id="hexo-deplayer-git"><a href="#hexo-deplayer-git" class="headerlink" title="hexo-deplayer-git"></a>hexo-deplayer-git</h2><p><strong>GitHub</strong>上传插件<br><code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p>
<h2 id="hexo-abbrlink"><a href="#hexo-abbrlink" class="headerlink" title="hexo-abbrlink"></a>hexo-abbrlink</h2><p><strong>生成唯一链接</strong><br><code>npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</code><br><strong>_config.yml</strong> 配置文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/</span><br><span class="line"># permalink_defaults:</span><br><span class="line">permalink: posts/:abbrlink.html</span><br><span class="line">abbrlink:</span><br><span class="line">  # alg: crc32 #算法： crc16(default) and crc32</span><br><span class="line">  rep: dec #进制： dec(default) and hex</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="生成站点地图SSR"><a href="#生成站点地图SSR" class="headerlink" title="生成站点地图SSR"></a>生成站点地图SSR</h2><p><code>npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</code><br><strong>_config.yml</strong> 配置文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># RSS订阅</span><br><span class="line">feed:</span><br><span class="line">  type: atom</span><br><span class="line">  path: atom.xml</span><br><span class="line">  limit: 20</span><br><span class="line">  hub:</span><br><span class="line">  content:</span><br><span class="line">  content_limit: 140</span><br><span class="line">  content_limit_delim: &#x27; &#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="本地搜索支持"><a href="#本地搜索支持" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索支持"></a>本地搜索支持</h2><p><code>$ npm install hexo-generator-searchdb</code><br><strong>_config.yml</strong> 配置文件<br>next在主题开启即可</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  content: true</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="日历插件"><a href="#日历插件" class="headerlink" title="日历插件"></a>日历插件</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/theme-next-calendar">https://github.com/theme-next/theme-next-calendar</a><br><code>npm install theme-next/theme-next-calendar</code><br>在next主题配置文件_config.yml配置</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CloudCalendar:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  language: zh-CN</span><br><span class="line">  single: true</span><br><span class="line">  root: /calendar/</span><br><span class="line">  calendarCdn: //cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-calendar/calendar.min.js</span><br><span class="line">  langCdn: //cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-calendar/languages.min.js</span><br><span class="line">  #disableSidebar: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
